The breakfast which is included is European style, breads, juice and coffee and some sliced meats and cheese.	Breakfast was basic and Italian style...just good coffee and brioche/bread, but I was happy with this, and if you're not, there are great cafes within minutes of the hotel, which has one of the very best loctions in Rome.	A simple breakfast comes with the room, bread, juice, coffee/tea, but if you are looking for something more you will need to go out.